data.title: A Wedding Party: Vintage Dresses and Formal Attire
data.meta_description: A Wedding Party: Vintage Dresses and Formal Attire will take place at the Pettengill-Morron House from 1 pm - 4 pm.
data.text:
A Wedding Party: Vintage Dresses and Formal Attire will be presented by the Peoria Historical Society at the Pettengill-Morron House (located at 1212 Moss Avenue in Peoria) from 1 pm – 4 pm. The exhibition will include gowns worn by Peoria Historical Society volunteers and feature wedding photos of former House resident Cynthia Stone and Hollywood actor Jack Lemmon, who were married in the parlor. Tickets are $10 and are available at https://309tix.com/

Featured the same day is the Peoria Historical Society’s Upscale Porch Sale at no cost. It is open to the public. Shop for jewelry, linens, china, crystal, antiques, artwork, new quilts and more.
